#  add_cppcheck(<target-name> [UNUSED_FUNCTIONS] [STYLE] [POSSIBLE_ERROR] [FORCE] [FAIL_ON_WARNINGS]) -
#    Create a target to check a target's sources with cppcheck and the indicated options
